desc: This is a modern apartment complex located just 800 meters past the Kiambu county head quarters and just 10 meters off the main Kiambu road next to Jaggers stage, its a 23 minutes drive from Nairobi. The seven spacious 2 bed roomed apartments gives privacy a new meaning ; a private rear kitchen and front balcony giving a panoramic view of the greenery in the neighborhood and from the horizon you can view the city of Nairobi sky crappers all from you balcony. The apartment boasts of high end finishes with wall to wall ceramics tiles on the floor, built in kitchen cabinets, wardrobes complete with a dressing table and a mirror, top of range ceramics in water closets and wash hand basins complete with a shaving unit light and mirror , stainless steel kitchen sinks complete with mixture taps, instant water heaters in the bathroom. The rooms have received three coats of light moss silk paint and brilliant white on the ceilings. The electrical fittings are of the best industry practice two way gang switches full and half moon lamps on the ceiling and walls of sitting and bedroom complete with bed switches on the latter numerous power sockets in every room. Externally kitchen balcony come with a dhobi sink and with terrazzo finish in the splash area. The balustrades and all the rails well done and in caterpillar green the common areas stair case in terrazzo finish and concrete in basement car park. We have 80,000 Liters underground water tank and 15000 liters overhead tanks fed by two mains supply making our supply constant a unique phenomenon in the area as most establishment do have water shortages. The security features unmatched in the area with a masonry high perimeter wall complete with an electric fence, razor wire and with tamper auto alarm. 24 hours professional Security guards supported by our motion sensor floodlights. Ample ground floor parking and play area for kids . You will be in a home not an apartment at the acacia. One unit available currently .
